Package hms.entity.record

Class AppointmentOutcomeRecord

java.lang.Object
hms.entity.record.AppointmentOutcomeRecord
public class AppointmentOutcomeRecord extends Object
Represents the outcome of an appointment, including prescribed medicines, consultation notes, and other relevant details.
